Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.43,0:01:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和父亲一起住的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.64,0:01:56.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:01:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:10.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第55话 石之花与七宝的初恋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  该不会是假情报吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.82,0:02:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种村落会有四魂碎片吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:23.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇也感受不到\N四魂碎片的气息吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  完全没有
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.43,0:02:28.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之还是散开来寻找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:30.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解散
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.68,0:02:37.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会\N想一个人去勾引女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.55,0:02:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒法师
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.02,0:02:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有妖怪的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.62,0:02:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  你这种态度对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.52,0:02:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:02:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦  犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明才刚开始找耶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:01.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有妖怪的话一闻就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:04.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本就是想偷懒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天气真好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.55,0:03:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇怪?七宝不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概跑去玩了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.25,0:03:21.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还是小孩子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.59,0:03:28.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉  真是让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.60,0:03:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这阵子一直不断战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.63,0:03:35.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偶尔也该让他们两人独处一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.97,0:03:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.51,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住  臭小子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不会被你们逮到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小偷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:47.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揍扁她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.18,0:03:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.12,0:03:52.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偷了我们家的柿子干对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.39,0:03:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才没有偷  你有看到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,闭嘴  你这骗子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.59,0:03:58.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙  等哥哥回来后
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会好好的修理你们一顿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.86,0:04:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.60,0:04:05.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你哥哥不是早就死在战场上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.37,0:04:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我父亲在他死前照顾他的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.44,0:04:10.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥才没有死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.87,0:04:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋  小偷还敢打人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.39,0:04:28.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼…赢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.07,0:04:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.34,0:04:48.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  狸猫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.91,0:04:50.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是狐狸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.28,0:04:51.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是帮助我的谢礼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要不要吃一半
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,偷来的柿子干
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.92,0:04:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:02.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来真的是这家伙不对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好厉害喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.59,0:05:08.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫五月  你呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:12.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我叫做七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.23,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝?好帅气的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.24,0:05:16.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我父亲帮我取的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.10,0:05:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此  你父亲是妖怪狸吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:20.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐狸啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是故意的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你有亲人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出生后不久就去世了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.62,0:05:34.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我还有一个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.89,0:05:38.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等他在战场立下大功
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.76,0:05:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成为武士后
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.89,0:05:41.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会回来迎接我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那刚才那些小鬼在撒谎咯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.04,0:05:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.54,0:05:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也会活着回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,特别让你看看  我的宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.91,0:05:59.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要对它许愿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何愿望都会实现
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很漂亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:07.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它叫做四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说是妖怪的宝贝碎片喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.07,0:06:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥  这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么愿望\N都能实现的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.44,0:06:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会成为武士的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.52,0:06:38.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥绝对不会说谎的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.53,0:06:48.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的吗?法师大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我家有妖怪盘踞着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.97,0:06:55.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  若没有尽早驱除的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:06:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是法师的义务
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不需要答谢我  名主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别这么说  各位的\N餐点与床铺已经准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.41,0:07:06.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弥勒那家伙又在唬人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.22,0:07:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:15.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.51,0:07:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的有妖怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:37.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是胡扯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.25,0:07:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.95,0:07:43.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.89,0:07:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.26,0:07:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝你居然知道这里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.39,0:07:53.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找这附近看起来最富裕
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.59,0:07:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又在做法事的人家准没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:59.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总…总之
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:01.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到四魂碎片了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.04,0:08:06.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.27,0:08:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是五月吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:18.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让姐姐看看你的碎片好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.42,0:08:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你该不会想抢走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:22.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要抢  如果是真的的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  坐下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.43,0:08:29.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没关系的  只是看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  如果是真的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.47,0:08:34.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就非拿走不可
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.04,0:08:37.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么一来五月的愿望就会…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.97,0:08:42.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么会判断的这么草率
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  笨蛋  我是大笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.15,0:08:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.15,0:08:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以了吧  我要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  路上小心喔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.52,0:08:56.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让她回去好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.29,0:09:01.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你还是不想来我们家吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.00,0:09:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.30,0:09:05.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哥哥现正在回来的路上呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.43,0:09:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇  那个碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  那是石之花
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.01,0:09:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,石之花?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.07,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是石英吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之是山上就能挖到的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:20.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根本不是四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.72,0:09:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是冒牌货啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.82,0:09:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.32,0:09:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月是个可怜的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥已经确定是战死的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.19,0:09:35.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她却不愿意相信
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,希望哥哥能快点回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我说由我们照顾她
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.34,0:09:46.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是她依然不肯离开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.44,0:09:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,曾经和哥哥一起生活的小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.21,0:09:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然被轰出了名主的家
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那小女孩可以利用
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.35,0:09:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我记住!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂拥有能创造\N奈落分身的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.57,0:10:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果向真正的碎片许愿的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.98,0:10:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月的哥哥就能活着回来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.91,0:10:59.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,图形好可怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.21,0:11:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:08.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:12.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉!你不是在睡觉吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.83,0:11:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这也是帮助人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.80,0:11:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别做梦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.93,0:11:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你也知道四魂之玉的可怕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.44,0:11:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是人类能使用的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.31,0:11:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  你为什么要偏袒那小女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.81,0:11:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,迷恋人家了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:34.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的脸长得蛮可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙  为了这么烂的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,少罗唆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.09,0:11:40.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我迷恋她
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.05,0:11:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在桔梗跟戈薇之间\N摇摆不定的你也没资格说我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去睡觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:54.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.75,0:12:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.18,0:12:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.69,0:12:19.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让你久等了 你过得好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直相信!我一直相信着!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.60,0:12:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥一定会回来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.21,0:12:42.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少应该向她道别
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.25,0:12:46.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月会不会一直\N对着假碎片祈祷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.79,0:12:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是我实在说不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.09,0:12:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,事情的真相…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.43,0:12:54.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.23,0:12:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.53,0:12:57.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的愿望实现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:08.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉  七宝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那叫做五月的女孩那边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.05,0:13:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真的很担心她呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.55,0:13:19.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月的哥哥早就不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.25,0:13:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她却深信假的碎片而等待着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.96,0:13:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.26,0:13:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又要多管闲事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.43,0:13:29.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.76,0:13:31.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.14,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看  虽然哥哥受了一点伤
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.07,0:13:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥真的回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.27,0:13:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.47,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是托你和四魂碎片的福
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.72,0:13:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么!妖怪?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.09,0:14:00.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥要快点治好伤口\N恢复精神喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊…让你吃了这么多苦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.70,0:14:07.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后哥哥会让你很幸福的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.07,0:14:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.48,0:14:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在名主家借宿的\N那一行人的伙伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.51,0:14:21.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.68,0:14:23.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能把那东西拿来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.62,0:14:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真正的四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.26,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放开五月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.99,0:14:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要做什么  哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.63,0:14:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂碎片的话
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里不就有一个吗  你看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.33,0:14:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不明白啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.93,0:14:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种烂石头一点用都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.27,0:14:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然将实现五月愿望的碎片…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点  矮子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去拿四魂碎片来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.52,0:14:59.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就扭断五月的脖子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.35,0:15:01.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:06.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是你哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.36,0:15:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现出原形吧  妖怪!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,狐火!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.53,0:15:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这小鬼真狠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.77,0:15:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来觉得当她哥哥也不错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.37,0:15:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.37,0:15:24.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋  我饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.55,0:15:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  快点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.33,0:15:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.97,0:15:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经被发现了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.47,0:15:56.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休想逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:15:57.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就用这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:16:00.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你先逃走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.48,0:16:03.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要  我怎么能这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.28,0:16:06.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只能一个人骑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.72,0:16:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:13.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逮到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是五月住的小木屋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.61,0:16:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,仔细看  是大肚子妖怪的杰作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:35.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少他们似乎是逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.95,0:16:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  弥勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.25,0:16:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之先追上七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们两人一定要平安啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是七宝的狐妖术
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.63,0:16:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是五月
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.64,0:17:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  云母
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.04,0:17:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝在妖怪那里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:05.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  走吧  戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你一定要平安逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小女孩逃走是没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.23,0:17:25.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矮子  我要拿你当人质
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.37,0:17:29.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去抢四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你一开始就应该找我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.37,0:17:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还刻意践踏五月的心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.08,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,浑蛋  我饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思  你想和我打吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.85,0:17:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那当然
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.52,0:17:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  消化液
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.66,0:17:50.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.96,0:17:53.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接招  爆雷筒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁现在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.63,0:18:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  你闹够了没有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.11,0:18:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的力量还是不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.78,0:18:20.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能跟大家一样战斗吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.66,0:18:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,游戏结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:36.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么  还没得到教训
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.94,0:18:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又变成奇怪的家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭家伙  你在找碴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.88,0:18:50.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刚刚好…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.42,0:18:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你试试刚领悟的爆流破
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.22,0:18:57.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭小子  你在胡说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将对手的妖气卷入风之伤中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.70,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让妖气逆流的必杀剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆流…啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.71,0:19:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶!对手的妖气太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.71,0:19:20.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爆流破根本就用不出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.71,0:19:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在罗哩叭唆什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太弱了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.85,0:19:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.99,0:19:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是昨晚从名主家中\N赶走的妖怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.74,0:19:49.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你这次相当努力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.98,0:19:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.51,0:19:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.25,0:19:56.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.48,0:19:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你解决了那只妖怪对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.72,0:20:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是我  是犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.46,0:20:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪就已经被扁得很惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.26,0:20:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.70,0:20:13.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这只妖怪知道打不过我们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.93,0:20:15.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想利用五月吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.74,0:20:18.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一牵扯到四魂碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.54,0:20:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都会遭遇不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.51,0:20:23.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都怪我忘的一干二净
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.54,0:20:26.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才让五月碰到这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.55,0:20:32.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.22,0:20:38.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:43.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.83,0:20:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:47.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要让名主大人照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实我已经知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.80,0:20:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥已经不在人世了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.95,0:21:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保重喔  五月
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你  七宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.32,0:21:08.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能遇见你真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.66,0:21:14.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五月  你一定要幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:18.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和你一样没有父母
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  我不是一个人活着
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.18,0:21:40.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  你是不是喜欢那孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.55,0:21:42.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.12,0:21:44.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是人小鬼大
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.62,0:21:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然小也是男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.29,0:21:50.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,初恋呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.90,0:21:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝  再拖拖拉拉就不理你喔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.50,0:21:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:30.70,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,除了真正珍贵的东西{\fad(500,0)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.04,0:22:42.18,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,若能全都舍弃 那该多好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:49.62,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,只是现实 往往是如此残酷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.59,0:22:53.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,但每当 遇到这种时刻
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.36,0:22:58.10,ED,NTP,0,0,0,,我只要紧闭双眼
